{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Blitz is a challenging, fast-paced platformer with infinite procedurally generated levels. Build a new unique character each run and fight one action-packed room after another! With multiple game modes you will be able to master movement, combat, and strategy in this fast paced experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316400/extras/Screenshot_2025-01-31_201746.png?t=1738374303\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Infinite Procedural Dungeons:</u></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No 2 dungeons are the same </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Maps get bigger and more difficult as you progress</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Replay Value (30+ hours of gameplay)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Many gameplay soundtracks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A wide range of level mutators and difficulty settings</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316400/extras/Screenshot_2025-01-31_202312.png?t=1738374303\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>Craft your Character:</strong></u></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build the ultimate character by leveling up to fit your playstyle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fluid Parkour System</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Over a dozen characters to play as</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Traits:</strong> Pick through dozens of unique traits to become more powerful</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Attributes:</strong>\u00a0Select one of the 5 main attributes upon level up (See Below)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Strength -</strong> Melee Damage, Kick Power, and Knockback</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dexterity -</strong> Ranged Damage, Reload Speed, Recoil Control, and Arrow Power</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Agility -</strong> Jump Height</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Speed -</strong> Movement Speed on ground and midair.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Sight -</strong> Overall Camera FOV</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316400/extras/Screenshot_2025-01-31_201555.png?t=1738374303\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>All the loot:</u></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Many many weapons <strong>(Guns, Bows, Swords, Rocket Launchers)</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find anvils and cauldrons around the map to craft</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Armor -</strong> Many Armor Types with increasing damage resistance</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Cover -</strong> Deploy cover to aid you in battle (A team to fight alongside you, a crate to shoot behind</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Throwables -</strong>\u00a0A boatload of Grenades, Spears, Blades, etc.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Gold -</strong> Use this to buy from traders</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316400/extras/Screenshot_2025-01-31_202017.png?t=1738374303\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>Advanced Ai with voicelines:</strong></u></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dozens of base enemies that evolve in further stages</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enemies level up and evolve like the character</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A wide range of difficulty settings for any skill level</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Npcs that you can hire</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Beasts that can be tamed</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Game Modes:</u></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dungeon:</strong> Fight your way through ominous procedurally generated dungeons, defeating one boss after the other. Find loot, trade with NPCs and craft your character into something unstoppable.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Survival:</strong> Survive wave after wave of enemies putting your movement and combat skill to the test.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The Climb:</strong> Similar to Jump Knight or Getting over it. Scale a huge vertical map in an attempt to obtain legendary status.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Gladiator:</strong>\u00a0Fight through increasingly difficult arenas, stacking gold and buying equipment to become stronger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316400/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738374303","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316400/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738374303","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316400/5f3e0651f54175c4bb251e799d2b32b815e78a51/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738374303","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316400/5f3e0651f54175c4bb251e799d2b32b815e78a51/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738374303","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Leaderboards","id":25}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3356110,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Blitz is a challenging, fast-paced pl